SubjectFinal Acts of the International Telecommunication Union World Radiocommunication Conference (Geneva, 2012) ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the FINAL ACTS OF THE INTERNATIONAL TELECOMMUNICATION UNION WORLD RADIOCOMMUNICATION CONFERENCE (Geneva, 2012).
